{"tha-ap502:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap502:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap502:0.3":"Piyalaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap502:1.1":"“Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap502:1.2":"vipine vicaram tada; ","tha-ap502:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap502:1.4":"sabbadhammana paragum. ","tha-ap502:2.1":"Piyalaphalamadaya, ","tha-ap502:2.2":"buddhasetthassadasaham; ","tha-ap502:2.3":"Punnakkhettassa virassa, ","tha-ap502:2.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap502:3.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap502:3.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap502:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap502:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap502:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap502:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap502:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap502:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap502:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap502:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap502:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap502:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap502:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap502:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma piyalaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap502:8.1":"Piyalaphaladayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap502:8.2":"Kinkanipupphavaggo pannasamo. ","tha-ap502:9.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap502:10.1":"Kinkani pamsukulanca, ","tha-ap502:10.2":"korandamatha kimsukam; ","tha-ap502:10.3":"Upaddhadussi ghatado, ","tha-ap502:10.4":"udakam thupakarako. ","tha-ap502:11.1":"Nalakari ca navamo, ","tha-ap502:11.2":"piyalaphaladayako; ","tha-ap502:11.3":"Satamekanca gathanam, ","tha-ap502:11.4":"navakanca taduttari. ","tha-ap502:12.1":"Atha vagguddanam ","tha-ap502:13.1":"Metteyyavaggo bhaddali, ","tha-ap502:13.2":"sakimsammajjakopi ca; ","tha-ap502:13.3":"Ekavihari vibhitaki, ","tha-ap502:13.4":"jagati salapupphiyo. ","tha-ap502:14.1":"Nalagaram pamsukulam, ","tha-ap502:14.2":"kinkanipupphiyo tatha; ","tha-ap502:14.3":"Asiti dve ca gathayo, ","tha-ap502:14.4":"catuddasasatani ca. ","tha-ap502:15.1":"Metteyyavaggadasakam. ","tha-ap502:16.1":"Pancamasatakam samattam. "}